OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1775592346
OL,3,CBanks in Jersey and Guernsey not
OL,4,Clegally required to offer basic
OL,5,Caccounts
OL,7,FThere are calls for Jersey and
OL,8,FGuernsey's governments to make banks
OL,9,Flegally obliged to offer islanders
OL,10,Fbasic bank accounts, even for those
OL,11,Fwith poor credit ratings.
OL,13,FCurrently, there is no legal
OL,14,Frequirement in either island to offer
OL,15,Fa basic bank account for those wishing
OL,16,Fto manage and protect their money.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1775592346
OL,3,CBanks in Jersey and Guernsey not
OL,4,Clegally required to offer basic
OL,5,Caccounts
OL,7,FSince 2015, the nine biggest personal
OL,8,Fcurrent account providers in the UK -
OL,9,Ffive of which operate in the islands -
OL,10,Fguarantee legal residents access to a
OL,11,Fbasic bank account.
OL,13,FIt leaves people unable to make
OL,14,Fpayments online and pay bills
OL,15,Fefficiently, and also causes security
OL,16,Fconcerns, as they have to carry cash.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1775592346
OL,3,CBanks in Jersey and Guernsey not
OL,4,Clegally required to offer basic
OL,5,Caccounts
OL,7,FSome businesses also do not accept
OL,8,Fcash. However, Jersey's States
OL,9,FAssembly recently voted in favour of a
OL,10,Fproposal to ensure islanders can
OL,11,Fcontinue to pay with notes and coins.
OL,13,FLee Madden struggled to access a bank
OL,14,Faccount when he went through a
OL,15,Fdifficult time in his life that
OL,16,Finvolved housing insecurity.
OL,18,FWhen he eventually found a job, he
OL,19,Fstill struggled to open a bank account.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1775592346
OL,3,CBanks in Jersey and Guernsey not
OL,4,Clegally required to offer basic
OL,5,Caccounts
OL,7,F"It was the embarrassment of the fact
OL,8,Fthat I couldn't open a bank account,"
OL,9,FLee told ITV News. "I couldn't get any
OL,10,Fwages paid to me."
OL,12,FHe added that he was rejected from all
OL,13,Fbanks he approached on the island, and
OL,14,Fthat the "stigma", "desperation", and
OL,15,F"frustration" made him believe he was
OL,16,Fleft with no option but to leave
OL,17,FJersey.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1775592346
OL,3,CBanks in Jersey and Guernsey not
OL,4,Clegally required to offer basic
OL,5,Caccounts
OL,7,FLee sought help from Community Savings
OL,8,FLimited, which offers basic banking
OL,9,Fservices to Channel Island residents
OL,10,Fwho may require additional help
OL,11,Faccessing accounts.
OL,13,FThe service allowed him to start
OL,14,Fgetting paid by his employer.
OL,16,F"There should be no stigma attached to
OL,17,Fasking for help," Lee added. "Our
OL,18,Fbanking system is part of our
OL,19,Fcommunity, and sometimes people need a
OL,20,Fbit of help and support".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1775592346
OL,3,CBanks in Jersey and Guernsey not
OL,4,Clegally required to offer basic
OL,5,Caccounts
OL,7,FStephen Reilly, CEO of Jersey's
OL,8,FCommunity Savings, said: "People who
OL,9,Fcome to us, they do feel a sense of
OL,10,Fshame or embarrassment about not being
OL,11,Fable to access something which people
OL,12,Ftake for granted, but is a basic human
OL,13,Fright to be able to operate your
OL,14,Ffinances in a bank account.
OL,16,F"If you've got a family, bills to pay,
OL,17,Fand you're responsible for the
OL,18,Ffinances in the house, then trying to
OL,19,Forganise finances without a bank
OL,20,Faccount is very difficult."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1775592346
OL,3,CBanks in Jersey and Guernsey not
OL,4,Clegally required to offer basic
OL,5,Caccounts
OL,7,FHe adds that regulatory legislation is
OL,8,F"not always the answer" and there
OL,9,Fneeds to be a more "open" dialogue on
OL,10,Fthe matter.
OL,12,FThere is currently no data on the
OL,13,Fnumber of unbanked islanders, which Mr
OL,14,FReilly believes creates greater
OL,15,Fbarriers to understanding the depth of
OL,16,Fthe issue.
OL,18,FWhat the islands' governments say
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1775592346
OL,3,CBanks in Jersey and Guernsey not
OL,4,Clegally required to offer basic
OL,5,Caccounts
OL,7,FJersey's Treasury Ministry, Deputy
OL,8,FElaine Millar, told ITV News that
OL,9,Ffollowing the UK's legislation would
OL,10,Fincur too many costs.
OL,12,F"Community Savings presents a more
OL,13,Ftargeted approach than just making
OL,14,Flegislation, which just makes banking
OL,15,Fmore difficult for everybody and
OL,16,Fpotentially drives up costs," Deputy
OL,17,FMillar explained.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1775592346
OL,3,CBanks in Jersey and Guernsey not
OL,4,Clegally required to offer basic
OL,5,Caccounts
OL,7,F"By legislating, you're adding to
OL,8,Fcompliance and financial burden,
OL,9,Fyou're adding to the cost of doing
OL,10,Fbusiness for the banks."
OL,12,FEd Ashton, Director of Operations for
OL,13,FSocial Security, States Housing &
OL,14,FInclusion in Guernsey, said the
OL,15,Fsuccess of Community Savings means
OL,16,FEmployment & Social Security has not
OL,17,Fconsidered introducing a legal right
OL,18,Ffor consumers to access a basic bank
OL,19,Faccount.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1775592346
OL,3,CBanks in Jersey and Guernsey not
OL,4,Clegally required to offer basic
OL,5,Caccounts
OL,7,FA statement from Mr Ashton reads:
OL,8,F"Guernsey Community Savings arrange
OL,9,Faccess to basic banking services for
OL,10,Fislanders who have been unable to open
OL,11,Fa retail bank account or if the bank
OL,12,Fhas closed their account.
OL,14,F"If a person without a bank account
OL,15,Fmakes a claim for benefits, the
OL,16,FCustomer Hub Team refers them to
OL,17,FGuernsey Community Savings for
OL,18,Fassistance in opening a basic bank
OL,19,Faccount.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1775592346
OL,3,CBanks in Jersey and Guernsey not
OL,4,Clegally required to offer basic
OL,5,Caccounts
OL,7,F"This has been a very successful
OL,8,Fapproach which has helped people to
OL,9,Faccess basic banking services who
OL,10,Fwould otherwise be excluded, including
OL,11,Fthose with poor credit history, ex-
OL,12,Foffenders and people with no fixed
OL,13,Faddress."
OL,15,FHow banks say they are supporting
OL,16,Fislanders
OL,18,FITV News contacted five main banks in
OL,19,Fthe Channel Islands: Barclays, Natwest/
OL,20,FRBS International, HSBC, Santander,
OL,21,Fand Lloyds International.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1775592346
OL,3,CBanks in Jersey and Guernsey not
OL,4,Clegally required to offer basic
OL,5,Caccounts
OL,7,FA spokesperson from Lloyds
OL,8,FInternational said in a statement: "We
OL,9,Fwork proactively with various
OL,10,Forganisations across the Channel
OL,11,FIslands and Isle of Man, as we believe
OL,12,Fthat having access to everyday banking
OL,13,Fis important.
OL,15,F"We offer a range of current accounts
OL,16,Fto meet different needs; we offer
OL,17,Faccounts for adults (above 18 years
OL,18,Fold) and young people (11 ` 18 years
OL,19,Fold) who are living in the Channel
OL,20,FIslands or the Isle of Man."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G12/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1775592346
OL,3,CBanks in Jersey and Guernsey not
OL,4,Clegally required to offer basic
OL,5,Caccounts
OL,7,FRBS International, through its NatWest
OL,8,FInternational brand, said it offers a
OL,9,Fbasic bank account in the form of the
OL,10,F"Foundation" account.
OL,12,F"The Foundation account is designed
OL,13,Ffor customers who may be financially
OL,14,Fvulnerable or unable to meet the
OL,15,Feligibility criteria for our standard
OL,16,Fproducts, so this product increases
OL,17,Faccess to essential banking services,"
OL,18,Fthey explained.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G13/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1775592346
OL,3,CBanks in Jersey and Guernsey not
OL,4,Clegally required to offer basic
OL,5,Caccounts
OL,7,F"As such, customers do not apply for
OL,8,Fthis account directly; instead, they
OL,9,Fare encouraged to apply for the Select
OL,10,Faccount, the bank's standard everyday
OL,11,Fcurrent account with no monthly fee.
OL,13,F"If their application is not
OL,14,Fsuccessful and we believe the
OL,15,FFoundation account would be more
OL,16,Fappropriate, it will be offered as
OL,17,Fpart of that process."
OL,19,FThey continued that the bank also
OL,20,Fprovides funding to Community Savings
OL,21,Fin both Jersey and Guernsey.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G14/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38615
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1775592346
OL,3,CBanks in Jersey and Guernsey not
OL,4,Clegally required to offer basic
OL,5,Caccounts
OL,7,FA Santander spokesperson told ITV News
OL,8,Fthat their CEO, James Pountney, is
OL,9,Fdeputy chair of Community Savings
OL,10,FLimited and that the bank works "very
OL,11,Fclosely with them, ensuring that bank
OL,12,Faccounts are accessible to everyone in
OL,13,Fthe community".
OL,15,FITV News did not receive official
OL,16,Fresponses from Barclays or HSBC.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G15/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
